T02D2805:163b-0: @163b * // 'phags pa thugs rje chen po yid du 'ong ba'i gzugs can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2805:163b-1: gzi brjid phung po mthong tsam gyis //
T02D2805:163b-2: skye bo kun gyi yid 'phrog cing //
T02D2805:163b-3: rgyal po'i ngag bzhin thams cad la //
T02D2805:163b-4: bsgos pa don yod byed rig bshad //
T02D2805:163b-5: thog mar brtan g-yo nam mkha'i sbyor ba yis //
T02D2805:163b-6: ngag bcad de las padma zla ba bskyed //
T02D2805:163b-7: de steng aa dang ka phreng ze'u 'bru can //
T02D2805:163b-8: 'dres gyur mgon po yid 'ong gzugs can bsgom //
T02D2805:163b-9: shel ltar rab dangs rdo rje lta bur mkhregs pa'i sku //
T02D2805:163b-10: dkar la dmar dangs shin tu 'od gsal rnam par
T02D2805:163b-11: dag / bltas pas mi ngoms dpe byad mtshan rab
T02D2805:163b-12: kun rdzogs pa // skyabs sbyin chu skyes g-yas g-yon phyag rgyas btab pa'o //
T02D2805:163b-13: brgya phrag 'od 'bar rgyan rnams las byung phan tshun 'od zer rnams 'khrugs pas //
T02D2805:163b-14: nyid kyi sku bkab dra ba dang ni dra ba phyed dang rdo rje g-yung drung 'khyil //
T02D2805:163b-15: zer phog pa dang gzugs brnyan rab 'dres tig tig gong bu 'khyil 'gyur te //
T02D2805:163b-16: spu sgo kun la rin chen 'od 'dzag mkha' la nyi ltar mdzes bdag gyur //
T02D2805:163b-17: de'i snying por yi ge gsum pa 'dus pa la nu ma gnyis kyis brgyan pa bltas la /
T02D2805:163b-18: dad pa dang lhan cig pa'i 'od kyi zhags pas
T02D2805:163b-19: po ta la nas gzhon nu 'bar ba nyid bkug
T02D2805:163b-20: la / bcu drug dang brgyad dang /
T02D2805:163b-22: bdun dang lnga la sogs pa'i lha mo lte ba'i
T02D2805:163b-23: sgo las mngon par 'phro ba'i mchod pa thams cad
T02D2805:163b-24: kyis yang dag par mchod nas /
T02D2805:163b-25: phyogs kyi gzhon nu ma bzhis yid 'ong mtshungs med
T02D2805:163b-26: la sogs pas bstod nas lcags kyu dang zhags pa
T02D2805:163b-28: dril bu'i rang bzhin gyis bkug cing bcug ste bcings la dgyes par bya'o //
T02D2805:164a-1: thugs ka dang ljags la yi ge bzhi dang bcu
T02D2805:164a-2: drug gi padmo dang 'khor lo nye bar bkod de
T02D2805:164a-3: / byams pa chen po'i yid kyis bzlas la /
T02D2805:164a-4: nam gyi tshe skye bo bdag gi ming thos pa dang /
T02D2805:164a-5: gzugs mthong bas dbang po mngon par g-yo ba'i tshe /
T02D2805:164a-6: de dag gi snying la hr'i: dmar po bsams nas /
T02D2805:164a-7: sna bug g-yas nas spros pa'i sa bon las 'od kyi mda' bkye ba bsnun te /
T02D2805:164a-8: de las bdud rtsi rgyun zags pas lus thams cad la khyab par bya'o //
T02D2805:164a-9: byams pa'i lta bas rnam blta zhing //
T02D2805:164a-10: rtag tu kun la snying rje 'jug / chags bral sdang ba yang med pa //
T02D2805:164a-11: sgrub po 'gro ba kun yid 'phrog / dbang po rab tu dul ba dang //
T02D2805:164a-12: dregs med bka' blo rab tu bde //
T02D2805:164a-13: 'jig rten mgon la lhag par dad //
T02D2805:164a-14: yid gzhungs gang yin skal ldan mtshan //
T02D2805:164a-15: ci ste 'di brtsams kyis ma spobs //
T02D2805:164a-16: de nas sbrang rtsi rma bya'i mdongs //
T02D2805:164a-17: me tog bzang po kun 'dab che //
T02D2805:164a-18: sbos chus sbyar ba smin mtshams byug / byang chub sems dkar dmar thig le //
T02D2805:164a-19: rgya mtsho'i wu ba seng ldeng spags //
T02D2805:164a-20: tsandan dmar po ga pur bcas //
T02D2805:164a-21: dpral bar byugs la gsang sngags brjod //
T02D2805:164a-22: spyan ras gzigs dpal yid 'ong mthus //
T02D2805:164a-23: dam bcas dam tshig rjes dran phyir //
T02D2805:164a-24: rtag pa'i rgyal po las byed 'dis //
